{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_05_beg","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":10,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_04_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-5","storyName":"祝福的歌谣","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"众人逃出石高原野，在迎向新生活的前夜，点起篝火，准备告别。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["风笛","苇草","塔拉流民","维恩","莫兰","塞尔蒙","陈","粗哑的歌声","年幼的流民","特别行动队士兵","菲舍尔"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g9_tent","screenadapt":"showall","id":5},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$normal_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"苇草，你那边固定了吗？","id":13,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，没问题。","id":15,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":16},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":18},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-90,0","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":19},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"-90,0","posto":"-90,-50","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":20},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_handcuff","volume":"0.7","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"shake","random":"false","power":"3","times":"8","isblock":"true","duration":"0.5","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":23},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"-90,-50","posto":"140,-50","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"shake","random":"false","power":"3","times":"5","isblock":"true","duration":"0.5","id":25},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":27},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"140,-50","posto":"0,-50","duration":"0.3","isblock":"true","id":28},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_flag","volume":"0.7","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":30},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#9","action":"jump","times":"2","power":"10","isblock":"true","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"咻——好了，这是最后一顶帐篷啦。","id":33,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#9"},{"type":"charslot","id":34},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"哎呀，你们俩的力气可真大。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"对了，你们是不是要走了？","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"是呀，我和陈陈要调查的就是那些被法术控制的“鬼魂士兵”，这边的事情结束之后，我们还有其他的任务。","id":39,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"而且这里已经是特伦特郡辖区的边界，应该不会再有驻军找你们麻烦啦。","id":40,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......唉，要是我们把秩序维持得更好一些，这么多混乱和冤枉的事情，就都不会发生了。","id":42,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"啊，你在说什么呢？要不是因为你们，我们都不知道能不能活到现在呢。","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"如果这是在我家，今晚我就要请你们喝接骨木酒，给你们送行。","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"不过我们现在手里的物资，大半还都是你们从......从那个“罗德岛”带过来的，哈哈。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"我们给那个罗德岛寄信，你们能收到不？到时候大家找到地方落脚了，跟你们说一声，你们要是再路过这附近，可以来做客。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"欸，应该可以吧？要是维多利亚的纷争结束，然后陈陈也见到了那个人......","id":49,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"......你呢，苇草？接下来你要去哪里？","id":51,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我......应该会确认所有人都安顿好了，再去做自己的事。","id":53,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"就算离开了石高原野，摆脱了罪名，没有了熄火钟的管制......塔拉人也依然生活在一片泥泞的土地上，他们还是会寸步难行。","id":55,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我觉得，我应该再帮他们想想办法。","id":56,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"塔拉和维多利亚的语言，我都会说，之后如果进入城市，遇到各种不同的人，我都可以交涉......会比其他人方便一些。","id":58,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"啊，对了，今天你去找罗德岛的安全屋时，有没有什么人跟踪你？","id":60,"figure":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......应该没有。","id":62,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"没关系，我记得你的提醒。如果那些士兵是冲我来的......我不怕。","id":63,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"还有......谢谢你的好心。","id":65,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":66},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":67},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":68},{"type":"Character","id":69},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_coldforest","screenadapt":"coverall","id":70},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":71},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":73},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"你说，到时候苇草肯不肯把帐篷卖一顶给我？","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"那可是城里工厂做出来的帆布，暴雨浇上半个月也不会漏水，正适合拿来改造我的小拖车。","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"她心地很善良，你也不会昧着良心出价。我猜，你们的交易应该是能谈成的。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"哈，我开玩笑的，我哪里有钱买这么好的东西。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"不过谁能想到呢，前几天我们还为怎么活命发愁，现在却能睡进工厂做出来的结实帐篷，夜里也能生火了......","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"嗯，她们很有本事。","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"也懂矿石病的事。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"（口哨声）","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"（不连贯的口哨旋律）","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"笼罩溪谷的雾霭啊......♪","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......将她远行的身影遮蔽......♪","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":96},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"还是很好听。","id":99,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......那些追过我的人里，现在应该只有你还记得我了。","id":101,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"别这么说......大家肯定都记得。","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"矿石病又不是你的错。","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"（有点跑调的口哨音）","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"唉。","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"那小子，塞尔蒙她哥，死了。说不定我们当时帮过的那一队深池都死了。","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我们白忙活了。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"还好......至少你还活着，失踪了那么久之后，你还活着。","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我看到苇草给你塞药了，矿石病是不是其实能治好？","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"不，她们都说是治不好的。","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"但是，请不要埋怨那些深池的士兵。我帮他们躲进工厂的运输车，伤口渗入了源石粗矿的碎屑......这也不是他们的错。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"没有，我哪有埋怨呀，我只是觉得心里难受。","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"你们都相信深池，可我不敢信。深池是比我们厉害，还有武器，但我们都亲眼看到了，最后那队人被打得有多惨。","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"深池会对塔拉人好，帮塔拉人出口气，可之后呢？我想不出来......我就只记得那天车厢上的血。","id":118,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"塞尔蒙到现在还是想去找深池，去跟维多利亚人打仗，我都劝不住她。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"你说，那天她跟苇草聊了那么久，苇草难道没给她讲清楚道理吗？","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"可是我觉得，塞尔蒙那么做，不坏。她那样的人，能为其他塔拉人做很多事。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"你还记得吗？我感染之后不久，整个感染者街区的人一起被驱赶出了小镇。","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"后来，被驱赶出来的镇民里更健壮有力的那些，抢走了大家身上所有的物资，留下了羸弱的老人与孩子，还有我这样在虚弱期的病人。","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......你该早点说。说出来至少心里没那么难过。","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"但其实，我都快记不清了。我都想不起来，为什么没人反抗，也没人保护其他人。","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"以前我一直想，生活就是这样子，手里捧着的无论是什么，只要肚子饿了，闭上眼睛就咽下去了。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"莉莎死在矿井底下，柯萝达也死在矿井底下，你们家难道有人抱怨过矿场的工作吗？","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"呃......我说不好，也许是不能抱怨谁，但至少大姐和二姐死的时候，我自己挺难过的。","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我想找人说说这些，但是又黑又闷的矿井底下，没人听我说。我跑出来兜售些杂货，结果每家人都有自己的难处，也没人听我说。","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"好吧，现在说也不迟。","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"是啊，现在也不迟。","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我们捡的这些木柴，应该够烧一晚上了。","id":140,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"（口哨声）......那就走吧，太阳落山了，等会儿你该看不清路了。","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":143},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"Character","id":146},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g9_tent","screenadapt":"coverall","id":147},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":148},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":150},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_242","focus":"2","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"哎，锅子咕嘟咕嘟冒泡啦，现在我能吃一口吗？","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_242","focus":"1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"别心急，你这傻子！难道你家里从来没让你烧过饭吗？","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"去帐篷里等着，等会儿肉煮好了我端过去。","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":156},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":157},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":159},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"她看起来心情好了不少。","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯......但她一定还是很伤心。","id":163,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"至少，让她死了去深池的心，是件好事。","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......你一直知道？","id":167,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我相信有你在的话，他们不会踏错路。","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......虽然你很难一直陪着这些人走，德拉克。","id":171,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":173,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我不会认错。","id":175,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":176},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"Character","id":180},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g10_tent_inside","screenadapt":"coverall","id":181},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":182},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":183,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":185},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","name2":"avg_npc_243","focus":"2","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"别瞎说，费加尔，去年的戏里，你演的是盖尔王的战士。你演他重伤倒下三次又爬起来三次，结果把自己的胳膊和腿都摔青啦。","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","name2":"avg_npc_243","focus":"1","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"那我今年就演他刀枪不入好啦。年年都演盖尔王战败，演加斯特里尔死在王城脚下，除了戏服上能缀点花，就再没新鲜的东西啦。","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"嘿，塞尔蒙，过来，坐过来。我看今年你可以扮演盖尔王手下第一大将军。虽然年纪小了点，但论气势，还真没人能盖过你。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"哈？","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","name2":"avg_npc_243","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"你就是馋她端来的锅子，才对她胡说。你看她自己都不愿意。","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"不是，你们在说什么啊？我不认识这人。","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"欸，你家那边到了夏天，不演那几出固定的剧目吗？我们在商量怎么分角色呢。","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"唔......演到最后，一个自称河神的家伙会站起来往观众身上洒水，那个活动？","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......见过，没兴趣参加，除非让我演河神。","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"那是河神在为死掉的战士哀悼呀。那段台词可比其他角色的都难记。","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#4$1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"啊。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"但也说不定我们还没建好房子，今年夏天就过去了。那你就能准备到明年。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#7$1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......是啊，说不定呢。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"看你这表情，你还想去找深池？","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"当然。你以为我跟你们一样，说放弃就放弃了？","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"这是那天我跟苇草聊过之后得出的结论。","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我还是相信，深池的梦想是可以实现的，也必须要有人去实现。","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":217},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":218},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"Character","id":221},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g9_tent","screenadapt":"coverall","id":222},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":223},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$normal_loop","volume":"0.4","id":224,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":225},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":226},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......你想从我这里打听什么？","id":228,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我没什么可过问。你做的事，我看在眼里。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我信我亲眼所见得出的判断，也信罗德岛的判断。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但现在大多数维多利亚人眼里，活着的德拉克，只有一条。","id":233,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......深池的红龙，塔拉的君主后裔。那一条红龙就足够让公爵们各怀鬼胎，贵族们人心惶惶。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你一定为难。","id":235,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"那......她知道我的身份吗？","id":237,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"风笛？","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"她其实很聪明，心也很细。但很多事，尤其是和她认同的朋友有关的事情，她不愿意往坏处想。","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":243,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这样同行下去的话，她迟早得面对，你也是。","id":245,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......你要劝我尽早离开吗？","id":247,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"做过的事情就是做过。需要你担负的责任，你逃不掉。","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但我觉得，对一些人而言，你是不是德拉克没那么重要。","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":252},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"粗哑的歌声","text":"细小的溪流梳过茵茵原野♪","id":254,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"粗哑的歌声","text":"我们为缺席的人举杯♪","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"歌声。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......应该是费加尔在唱歌。","id":259,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":261,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"塔拉语？","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1"},{"type":"Charact